"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-celebrity-news-1933944-Ellie-Simmonds-Olympics-Strictly-scandal\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Express.co.uk exclusively spoke toEllie Simmondsabout the struggles she faced during the Paralympics, leading to her decision to exit competitive sport aged just 21.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toEllie Simmondsabout\", \"from\": 32, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \"the struggles\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 67}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 100}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 113, \"to\": 125}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive sport\", \"from\": 134, \"to\": 151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The swimming ace - now a BAFTA-winning documentary film maker and TV presenter - also revealed that her intense training routine in her younger years had led her to miss out on \\\"growing up\\\".\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The swimming ace\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 185}, {\"ngram\": \"- now a BAFTA-winning documentary film maker\", \"from\": 186, \"to\": 230}, {\"ngram\": \"TV presenter\", \"from\": 235, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"her intense training routine\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"her younger years\", \"from\": 301, \"to\": 318}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was growing up in [professional] sport and in the spotlight and feeling the pressure...\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"[professional] sport\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 401}, {\"ngram\": \"the spotlight\", \"from\": 409, \"to\": 422}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 435, \"to\": 447}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was just burnt out,\\\" she explained.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 488, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We had an individual on the team who was not the nicest and treated us not in a nice way.\", \"from\": 490, \"to\": 580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an individual\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice way\", \"from\": 569, \"to\": 579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why I took the decision afterwards to take a year out from the sport,\\\" Ellie continued.\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 599, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"a year\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 637}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 656}, {\"ngram\": \"Ellie\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was lucky that I could make that decision - but career changes, or just saying no to things, is okay - to look after your mental health and look after yourself.\\\"\", \"from\": 676, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that decision\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"career changes\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 764, \"to\": 770}, {\"ngram\": \"okay\", \"from\": 775, \"to\": 779}, {\"ngram\": \"your mental health\", \"from\": 796, \"to\": 814}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of agonising over it, she opted to take a break from the difficult and pressurised workplace environment - and ended up having \\\"the best year that I have ever had\\\".\", \"from\": 842, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficult and pressurised workplace environment\", \"from\": 903, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"the best year\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She used the time to go travelling everywhere from diverse places in the UK to the picturesque island of Madagascar, where she went without any phone signal for an entire 24 hours.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.99932280536751, \"rank\": 0.0006775989336564779, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1120, \"end\": 1130, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madagascar\", \"score\": 0.9988613128667382, \"rank\": 0.0011302035571971413, \"text\": \"Madagascar\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madagascar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madagascar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1024, \"to\": 1032}, {\"ngram\": \"diverse places\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"the picturesque island\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"any phone signal\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"an entire 24 hours\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The digital detox helped her to pause, focus on \\\"the beautiful world that we live in\\\" and \\\"find that confidence of being okay on my own\\\" while doing so.\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The digital detox\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1214}, {\"ngram\": \"the beautiful world\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"that confidence\", \"from\": 1293, \"to\": 1308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though she travelled solo, she wasn't lonely for a second, and ended up \\\"making friends all around the world\\\".\", \"from\": 1350, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"friends\", \"from\": 1430, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Ellie Simmonds' dance partner's advice after crippling nerves on Strictly Ellie can not relate to the traumatic Strictly experience that contestants likeSherlock'sAmanda AbbingtonandLove Island'sZara McDermotthave reported, asshe had a perfect partnership with her pro dance partner, Nikita Kuzmin.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1773, \"entit