29}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2085}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"TV viewers\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since her permanent retirement from sport after the Tokyo Olympics and her decision to go into TV fulltime instead, Ellie feels the pressure is off - something she especially notices when reporting on events like theOlympic Gamesas a presenter.\", \"from\": 2114, \"to\": 2358, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her permanent retirement\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2144}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2155}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2180}, {\"ngram\": \"her decision\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2197}, {\"ngram\": \"TV fulltime\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2220}, {\"ngram\": \"Ellie\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2235}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2254}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympic Gamesas\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2345}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do not miss:Strictly star Ellie Simmonds opens up about how rejection made her successful Do not miss:Strictly star in tears questioning who she'd be 'if I had not been adopted' Do not miss:BBC Strictly star Ellie Simmonds 'splits' from childhood sweetheart Matt Dean \\\"I am going to have the easy job in a sense now.\", \"from\": 2360, \"to\": 2681, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2386, \"end\": 2400, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Simmonds\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ellie Simmonds\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Simmonds\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ellie_Simmonds\"}, {\"begin\": 2552, \"end\": 2555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9983266409140481, \"rank\": 0.001648451892462041, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q2